From Robert Andolina Subject Sabres Bruins Buffalo fans Some people in the discussion group, as well as commentator Al on ESPN, believe that game is critical for the Sabres HELLOOOO The Sabres are AHEAD games to , not behind As a life long Sabres fan, I am well aware of their ability to choke, but let's not exaggerate that As long as the Sabres win one of the next games be it game OR game , they are still in good shape ahead games to , with game to be played at Buffalo If they lose games three AND four, then start worrying Game is critical for Boston, not Buffalo Rob Andolina